tool_description: API tool for collecting user feedback.
name: Feedback-api
title: Feedback-api

api_list.name: getFeedback
api_list.description:
### Get list of feedback for analytics
Various filters can be applied in query parameters.

optional_parameters.name: userId
optional_parameters.description: User ID to filter by. Example: "abc-xyz".

optional_parameters.name: userIP
optional_parameters.description: IP address to filter by. Example: "91.201.190.10".

api_list.name: getFeedbackById
api_list.description: ### Get concrete feedback by id for analytics
